The paper discusses optimization techniques in computer science, specifically in the area of Optimization Modulo Theories (OMT) and MaxSMT. This falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) as well as Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO). The use of sorting networks also suggests a connection to Data Structures (cs.DS) and Programming Languages (cs.PL). Finally, the empirical evaluation of different techniques involves Software Engineering (cs.SE).
